---
// PricePanel.astro - A panel that shows pricing and purchase information
---

<div
  class="h-full w-full overflow-y-auto rounded-xl bg-gray-100 font-sans text-gray-900 shadow-xl dark:bg-gray-600 dark:text-white"
>
  <div class="space-y-6 p-6">
    <div class="align-center flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <img
          src="/images/hv_main_logo.svg"
          alt="ComputeSDK Logo"
          class="h-8 w-auto"
        />
        <h2 class="ml-2 text-xl font-bold">Operator</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        $998/yr
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">What's included?</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mr-2 mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          The code (system requirements)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mr-2 mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          Easy installation (8-minute video)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mr-2 mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          Free updates to any 1.x version
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mr-2 mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          Bare bones support included
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4 dark:border-gray-700">
      <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold">How do we get it?</h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        After you purchase, we'll email you a private download link that
        includes everything you need.
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://buy.stripe.com/test_bJedR2g3p0YD34S0lY5AQ00"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        <button
          class="w-full rounded-lg bg-[#19874d] py-5 text-xl font-extrabold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#19874d]/80"
        >
          Checkout
        </button>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
